org.clafer.choco.constraint

Class OrConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.constraints.Constraint<solver.variables.Variable,solver.constraints.Propagator<solver.variables.Variable>>
      • org.clafer.choco.constraint.OrConstraint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, solver.propagation.IPriority

    public class OrConstraint
extends solver.constraints.Constraint<solver.variables.Variable,solver.constraints.Propagator<solver.variables.Variable>>
    Boolean or. The difference between this constraint and the one provided by the library is that this one does not reify to boolean variables, thus it can be added after the search has started. The one provided in the library requires dynamic variable addition which is not supported.

    jimmy
